    "However, the gap between anticipated benefits and actual outcomes, such as the limited direct improvements in patient outcomes, highlights ongoing challenges.",
    "This discrepancy emphasizes the need for a focused evaluation of how GenAI tools can directly impact patient health and care quality.",
    "Emerging LLM applications in medical education, decentralized trials, and digital twin technologies (i.e., virtual replicas of physical systems used for real-time simulation and analysis in healthcare) suggest an expanding scope for these tools.",
